overview: On this episode of Hitting the Highspots Rob Naylor sits down with ECW original Chris Hamrick. To say this is a shoot is an understatement as Hamrick rips into everybody from Hulk Hogan to Bret Hart to your momma. This is one of the wildest if not the wildest episode of Hitting the Highspots of all time. Sit back and get ready to fly high with Naylor and Chris Hamrick.
title: Hitting The Highspots - Chris Hamrick
